    <item>
      <title>中国说，我们欠芬太尼的“非常感谢”，敦促谈话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/china-says-us-owes-big-thank-you-on-fentanyl-calls-for-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，这已经有力地打击了芬太尼贸易，并谴责了唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税，因为世界上两个最大的经济体在任何降温紧张局势的情况下仍处于矛盾之处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/china-says-us-owes-big-thank-you-on-fentanyl-calls-for-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 09:46:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普向德黑兰发出信件时，中国主持伊朗核谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/china-to-host-russia-and-iran-for-talks-on-moribund-nuclear-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普敦促德黑兰就其原子能工作或面临军事行动进行新协议时，将与伊朗和俄罗斯进行核谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/china-to-host-russia-and-iran-for-talks-on-moribund-nuclear-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 08:41:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>劫持火车后，巴基斯坦军队杀死了所有武装分子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/pakistan-army-kills-27-militants-as-hundreds-still-held-on-train</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自周二自周二在Bal路支省西南部以来，巴基斯坦安全部队与持有火车及其乘客人质的叛乱分子交换了所有武装分子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/pakistan-army-kills-27-militants-as-hundreds-still-held-on-train</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 05:55:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EPA终止了200亿美元的气候项目赠款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/trump-s-epa-terminates-20-billion-in-grants-for-climate-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该环境保护局表示，将终止通过前总统乔·拜登（Joe Biden）的签名气候法制定的绿色银行计划授予的200亿美元赠款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/trump-s-epa-terminates-20-billion-in-grants-for-climate-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 01:34:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
